FuncDef: This command removes the most recent change(s) done to the candidate. The changes can be reapplied using theredocommand. All undo/redo history is lost when the operator exists edit-cfg mode. Undo can not be used to recover a candidate that has been discarded withcandidate discard.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the number of previous changes to remove. Values-1 to 50. ParamDefault: Default- 1
